### 负荷监控接口测试

### 1. 获取电力仪表列表
GET http://localhost:8080/energy/realtime/getModulesByDimension?dimensionCode=A02A02A01&energyType=1&includeChildren=true
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 查询负荷时序数据 - 按天（每小时一个数据点）
POST http://localhost:8080/energy/realtime/getLoadTimeSeriesData
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleIds": ["yj0001_1202", "yj0001_1203"],
  "timeGranularity": "day",
  "queryDate": "2025-07-25",
  "startTime": "2025-07-25 00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-07-25 23:59:59"
}

### 2.1 查询负荷时序数据 - 按月（每天一个数据点）
POST http://localhost:8080/energy/realtime/getLoadTimeSeriesData
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleIds": ["yj0001_1202", "yj0001_1203"],
  "timeGranularity": "month",
  "queryDate": "2025-07",
  "startTime": "2025-07-01 00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-07-31 23:59:59"
}

### 2.2 查询负荷时序数据 - 按年（每月一个数据点）
POST http://localhost:8080/energy/realtime/getLoadTimeSeriesData
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleIds": ["yj0001_1202"],
  "timeGranularity": "year",
  "queryDate": "2025",
  "startTime": "2025-01-01 00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-12-31 23:59:59"
}

### 3. 获取实时负荷状态
POST http://localhost:8080/energy/realtime/getCurrentLoadStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleIds": ["yj0001_1202", "yj0001_1203"]
}

### 3.1 获取实时负荷状态 - 测试单个仪表
