### 5. 原有的时序数据查询接口（保持兼容）
POST http://localhost:8080/energy/realtime/getTimeSeriesData
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "moduleIds": ["yj0001_1202", "yj0001_1203"],
  "parameters": [1, 2, 3],
  "timeGranularity": "day",
  "queryDate": "2025-07-25",
  "startTime": "2025-07-25 00:00:00",
  "endTime": "2025-07-25 23:59:59"
}

### 6. 原有的实时状态查询接口（保持兼容）
